title: Episode 15: Death and Dying (with Dr. Illene Cupit)
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this episode we talk with UW-Green Bay Human Development and Psychology faculty member, Dr. Illene Cupit, about her research on death, dying, and loss.  Her research assistants, Danielle DiCarlo, Lisa Barnaby, and Michelle McChesney, also share their insights into the topic.
